Step1) Download git and configure.
Step2) Jahape bhi gitbash use karna hai uss folder mein jakar Right click>> use Git Bash here
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Commands)
C1) git init >>>>Initialised the empty git repo
C2) git status >>>> btata hai current folder mein kitni files untracked hai ,, , kitni staged and kitni commited hai.
C3) git log >>> file ka history btata hai
C4) git add . >>>> add all the files... to STAGING
C5) git add file_name.extension  >>>> specific file name to STAGING
C6) git commit -m >>> commit all the files in the staging area
C7) git reset <commit hash key> >>>> pheechle commit pe le jayega
C8) git stash >>>> commit bhi nahi karega but stage karne ke baad  ... kind off backstage rakhega